1 Python2切换到Python3
echo alias python=python3 >> ~/.bashrc
source ~/.bashrc

2 Python3切换到Python2
gedit  ~/.bashrc
alias python=python3 
source ~/.bashrc

3 查看版本
python -V

4.查看pip版本
pip show pip 

5.更新pip版本
#python -m pip install --upgrade pip

#wget https://bootstrap.pypa.io/get-pip.py
#sudo python get-pip.py

#python -m pip install -U pip


6.Ubuntu升级pip后，使用时出现了问题：

Traceback (most recent call last):
  File "/usr/bin/pip", line 9, in <module>
    from pip import main
 解决方法：
打开终端，在终端中输入

sudo gedit /usr/bin/pip
这时打开了pip文件，修改

from pip import main  
if __name__ == '__main__':  
    sys.exit(main()) 
为

from pip import __main__  //修改
if __name__ == '__main__':  
    sys.exit(__main__._main())//修改

7.安装selenium时出现
ERROR: Could not install packages due to an EnvironmentError: [Errno 13] Permission denied: '/usr/local/lib/python3.5/dist-packages/selenium-3.141.0.dist-info'
Consider using the `--user` option or check the permissions.

解决方法：pip install selenium --user
后面加上user即可

8.googledriver 在/usr/bin

9.google 出现Failed to load extension from manifest file ismissing or un...
解决办法：
find ~ -name "*chrome*.desktop"
#and then after looking at the list and maybe looking inside the files and deciding
#that you are ok with deleting them just to see if this fixes it....
find ~ -name "*chrome*.desktop" | xargs rm
#or something like
find ~ -name "*chrome*.desktop" | xargs gvfs-trash
#or maybe just save them in a folder or rename them while you make sure
#this is the problem


